==English==
Blad is a British Slang word used in much the same way as dude or man is used in American slang, this slang word Is rumoured to have roots in Jamaican and even Russian language or as an evolution of the word blood as in "blood brother". In Australia, Blad was adopted around Febuary 2006 but reverted back to the word [[lad]] for unknown reasons.

